title: Neil Young & Crazy Horse Sunday, March 10, 2013, Sydney
description:
Neil Young & Crazy Horse -
Sunday, March 10, 2013, Sydney Entertainment Centre,
Sydney, Australia.

Equipment: Tascam DR-07 MK II using the internal microphones.
Location: Floor (Standing), dead centre, 25 metres from the stage.
Sound Quality: Good.

The decision was made to include the entire (29:06) min/sec of the "The Alchemists Appear And Begin Scurrying Around The Stage" segment, as i felt it added to the overall completeness of the show (for me anyway).
The same recording level was used throughout the entire concert, which will explain why the "The Alchemists Appear And Begin Scurrying Around The Stage" segment, is lower in volume when you listen to it.
